<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PeruTM5.1">
<l>tarutuyaran taṭāyēluṉ caraṇallāl caraṇillai</l>
<l>viraikuḻuvu malarpoḻilcūḻ viṟṟuvakkōṭ ṭammāṉē</l>
<l>yariciṉattā līṉṟatā yakaṟṟiṭiṉum maṟṟavaṭṭaṉ</l>
<l>ṉaruḷniṉaintē yaḻuṅkuḻavi yatuvēpōṉ ṟiruntēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>There is no refuge [for me] other than Your feet</l>
<l>[although You] do not curb the grief [that You] give [me],</l>
<l rend="indent">O Lord of Viṟṟuvakkōṭu, surrounded by groves with blossoms mingled with fragrance!</l>
<l>Even though the mother who gave [him] birth casts [him] aside out of cutting anger</l>
<l>the infant cries thinking of her benevolence again.</l>
<l>I have been like that.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
